Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.51,1:33:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've made it important in your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.85,1:33:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In and of itself, it's probably of no importance to the evolution of mankind in the latest.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.31,1:33:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not important to evolution of mankind?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.39,1:33:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.55,1:34:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a blimp on the.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.23,1:34:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Radar screen, like other wars and things, is just something that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.65,1:34:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Man has been at war 97% of recorded time.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.33,1:34:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should he change?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.07,1:34:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.98,1:34:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.36,1:34:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender to God, not.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.00,1:34:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying, am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.54,1:34:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.26,1:34:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,97% of recorded history, man has been at war.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.50,1:34:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.62,1:34:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He makes all kinds of money.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.20,1:34:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He makes all, he becomes famous.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.48,1:34:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He becomes a hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.74,1:34:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He becomes Napoleon.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.78,1:34:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He becomes the victim.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.56,1:34:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the payoff of war is tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.24,1:34:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The profits to me made are dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.94,1:34:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One defense contract is worth billions, billions.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.25,1:34:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.02,1:34:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell me how you're going to bring it to an end, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.73,1:34:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When you figure it out, give me a call.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.16,1:35:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The glamour of war, the glamour of it, the parades, the macho.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.94,1:35:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so today you said something.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.24,1:35:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just depend on the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.06,1:35:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because it fluctuates, it rises and subsides.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.98,1:35:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was at 207, it dropped to 204.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.08,1:35:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, if we can't depend on the evolution of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.36,1:35:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when consciousness is all that exists, how can we not depend on it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.36,1:35:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do we depend on?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.52,1:35:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're mixing levels there.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.01,1:35:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness is an infinite field of energy, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.85,1:35:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.59,1:35:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.45,1:35:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Human consciousness is just one expression of it, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.26,1:35:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the same thing as the infinite field of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.22,1:35:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,which is nonlinear and doesn't have any content, much less humanness,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.04,1:36:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but it does incorporate humanness as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.10,1:36:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the question again?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.00,1:36:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we're depending on the evolution of human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.88,1:36:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't depend on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.86,1:36:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything about depending on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.60,1:36:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, you said we can't just depend.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.16,1:36:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of the sea is this high and now it's this high.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.32,1:36:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't depend on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.82,1:36:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.20,1:36:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do we depend on?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.14,1:36:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own self.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.08,1:36:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.44,1:36:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own spiritual awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.44,1:36:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, which is my consciousness, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.44,1:36:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yours, not the world's.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.88,1:36:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about consciousness as an abstract universality.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.40,1:36:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, or collective.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.58,1:36:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about collective.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.44,1:36:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own personal consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.82,1:36:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I never say anything about depending on the overall level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.40,1:36:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The overall level of consciousness was 207 calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.68,1:36:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's 204, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.98,1:36:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.28,1:36:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't know what you mean by depending on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.66,1:36:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean expecting it to constantly get better was a false premise.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.42,1:37:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes up and apparently it also goes down.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.36,1:37:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but isn't it like anything that we, you know, thoughts arise, they subside.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.56,1:37:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's times that we make quantum leaps in our life.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.46,1:37:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.60,1:37:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's times we fall back.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.28,1:37:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But then when we move forward, we're usually going further than where we were before we...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.10,1:37:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.30,1:37:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be and could be not, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.34,1:37:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.66,1:37:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes and no.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.49,1:37:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.49,1:37:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.07,1:37:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't depend on it, in other words, is what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.51,1:37:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.25,1:37:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If the consciousness level has dropped, could it be that someone of a high calibration has left the planet
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.53,1:37:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and that no one has replaced him at that time?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.63,1:37:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.24,1:37:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.62,1:37:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.05,1:37:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.52,1:37:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show him.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.07,1:37:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll mess with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.83,1:37:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to Chase.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.53,1:38:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I want you to read this to him so that he'll sign it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.82,1:38:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He signed it twice, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.34,1:38:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, I work with cancer patients in intensive care, cancer hospital,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.76,1:38:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and I drive two hours a day and I listen to your tapes and all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.08,1:38:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that helpful to keep listening to them?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.90,1:38:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm obsessed with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.98,1:38:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people do.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.84,1:38:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I listen to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.50,1:38:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes second nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.62,1:38:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.92,1:38:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.48,1:38:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.48,1:38:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They learn it by familiarity, and then through familiarity, it just seems obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.93,1:38:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, well, that's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.50,1:38:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's helpful.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.24,1:38:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it all along, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.70,1:38:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That also would be helpful to the patients.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.08,1:38:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're not doing it...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.08,1:38:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, yes, of course, everything...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.54,1:38:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, if your consciousness advances, you're going to be of greater benefit to the patients, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.36,1:38:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.76,1:38:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.68,1:38:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.00,1:38:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.70,1:39:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I would have patients hanging on to life because they...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.14,1:39:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't have permission to leave, and I'd say, you know, it's okay to die, it's okay to let go of the body, it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.71,1:39:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your pictures.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.25,1:39:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.93,1:39:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.43,1:39:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And they go, oh, and die.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.93,1:39:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're hanging on for the family, they're hanging on for all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.00,1:39:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say, it's okay to leave, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.52,1:39:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.85,1:39:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.73,1:39:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to thank Susan for making sure you keep...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.90,1:39:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep eating, and that...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.42,1:39:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And that you don't wear shirts with holes in them.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.54,1:40:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he still does.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.98,1:40:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He does.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.38,1:40:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.64,1:40:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of weeks ago, meditating, I was totally blank, which in itself is a little unusual.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.76,1:40:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I had a very, very strong picture in my mind of going...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.80,1:40:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was up in an elevator, and there were streaks of light, so I could visualize going up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.22,1:40:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I kept going up and up, and then the thought came to me, gee, maybe I'm going to have a knowingness when I hit 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.16,1:40:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.18,1:40:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that instant, the picture left.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.28,1:40:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.69,1:40:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that meaningful at all?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.53,1:40:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.55,1:40:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.35,1:40:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.35,1:40:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.05,1:40:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.65,1:41:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What meaning does it have?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.27,1:41:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.88,1:41:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What meaning does it have?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.60,1:41:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What does level 500 mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.18,1:41:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, 500 to me means loving.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.42,1:41:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.00,1:41:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, that you let go of anything that is non-loving in your life, and dedicate your life to loving this, which is really the fastest way to God that I know of.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.69,1:41:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To let go of that which is ungodly.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.11,1:41:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.83,1:41:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When I hit 500, will I have a knowingness, or just I'll be there and...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.17,1:41:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need a knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.59,1:41:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.21,1:41:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.92,1:41:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I love my new dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.46,1:41:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My new dog loves me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.82,1:41:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of us need a knowingness, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.04,1:41:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is it wussy-wussy, and the dog goes wussy-wussy, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.32,1:41:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to hear about my dog?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.38,1:41:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about five minutes right there, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.96,1:41:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.36,1:41:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You just enjoy the reality of what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.14,1:41:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When you notice the beauty of all of nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.28,1:41:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stunning.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.91,1:42:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're just awesome.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.23,1:42:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, you say, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.89,1:42:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.61,1:42:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at the bark of that tree, and how it is, and you can see that it's almost breathing, and it comes as a revelation, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.11,1:42:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've almost had that experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.13,1:42:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're close to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.15,1:42:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.71,1:42:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.15,1:42:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.33,1:42:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.85,1:42:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, God's love.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.17,1:42:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all well.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.27,1:42:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.06,1:42:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Small gift for you, Susie.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.60,1:42:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.48,1:42:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.08,1:42:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time I was here, I didn't have a question for you, and I left experiencing, for the first time in my life, something that I understood to be unconditional loving.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.33,1:42:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just feel enormous gratitude for having been in the presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.79,1:42:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I did have a question as well about contemplation and meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.44,1:43:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You recommend contemplation, but you also speak about...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.72,1:43:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard you on one occasion say you recommend everyone to do some meditating, and I was wondering what you recommend, and then I thought...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.72,1:43:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's meditation and contemplation, and I think contemplation is more useful in many ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.82,1:43:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The meditation, you usually set aside a time of the day and a certain place and a certain style, and it sort of removes you from the ongoing course of daily life.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.04,1:43:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, if your life gets...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.18,1:43:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If your life gets very busy, what happens is the time assigned to meditation gets smaller and smaller.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.08,1:43:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, you know, you can't really...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.90,1:43:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to catch the subway in time.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.34,1:43:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sort of skip it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.96,1:43:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more vulnerable, although I did it for many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.62,1:44:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplation is more a lifestyle, a lifestyle in which you relate to life through the level of awareness, consciousness awareness itself, rather than focused meditation.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.07,1:44:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you had an actual...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.15,1:44:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What type of meditation that you'd recommend for someone who...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.27,1:44:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's a classic Zen meditation, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.99,1:44:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's classic.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.87,1:44:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the First Zen Institute back in the 1950s.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.74,1:44:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget what it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.20,1:44:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.38,1:44:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They said we could go 15 minutes over.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.52,1:44:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They changed it, and we're already 10 over, so yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.12,1:44:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, so if we have to come to an end, we will come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.68,1:44:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what time they said we should leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.04,1:44:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.40,1:44:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're happy to be cooperative in any way that serves the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.42,1:45:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What a blessing to be here with you all this beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.70,1:45:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually we've got some beautiful music that we can conclude with, but you know it's the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.21,1:45:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.34,1:45:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold intention in mind to see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.78,1:45:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.21,1:45:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderment.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.32,1:45:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.78,1:45:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So many make...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.55,1:45:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent people here all at one time.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.06,1:45:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We join together, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.92,1:45:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We join together as a very far powerful force to counteract the negativity of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.39,1:45:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.48,1:45:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.96,1:46:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.98,1:46:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Be that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.74,1:46:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Be that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.78,1:46:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.51,1:46:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.95,1:46:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you do, the world resists.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.30,1:46:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to save the world, it's going to resist you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.35,1:46:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably have you arrested and assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.85,1:46:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.42,1:46:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We influence everything by what we have become.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.74,1:46:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Become the ultimate fulfillment of what you know your spiritual capacity is, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.75,1:46:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That way we bless all of human life.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.72,1:46:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing they can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.70,1:46:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you raise the level of the sea, you raise the level of all the ships at sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.04,1:46:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the human ego wants to do is go around lifting ships.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.08,1:46:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll lift this ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.14,1:46:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll lift this ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.86,1:46:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll save these people and lift this ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.44,1:47:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.26,1:47:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Very expensive.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.82,1:47:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Catastrophic.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.10,1:47:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to save the people in foreign countries.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.76,1:47:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to first save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.74,1:47:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we do is by unconditional lovingness, we try to lift the level of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.58,1:47:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you raise the level of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.84,1:47:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you raise the level of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.58,1:47:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you raise the level of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.80,1:47:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you raise the level of the sea, you raise the level of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.40,1:47:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You raise every ship afloat without having to lift one single ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.22,1:47:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So our lovingness radiates forth into the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.94,1:47:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The world can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.82,1:47:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The world can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.96,1:47:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you choose to be forgiving and love and try to see the upside of everyone,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.99,1:47:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,even those who are insanely wicked, you say, I'm sorry, oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.66,1:47:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The only pleasure they have is to be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.76,1:48:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The only pleasure they have is left is that of wickedness.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.86,1:48:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, how pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.21,1:48:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.07,1:48:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The only pleasure you have left is the suffering of others.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.83,1:48:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the most pathetic condition I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.89,1:48:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Forsaken completely by God, by your own rejection of divinity, denial of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.33,1:48:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.40,1:48:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We all give thanks for our existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.71,1:48:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, let's just go like this and say, silently in our mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.24,1:48:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the old.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.22,1:48:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, for my existence, the great gift of life itself, do I treasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.59,1:48:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I give thanks to thee, oh, Lord, in the name of all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.52,1:49:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's all we can do for the human condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.24,1:49:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think we've just done what we can do for the human condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.36,1:49:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.46,1:49:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To bless everyone with unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.55,1:49:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if there's anything more we can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.64,1:49:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.14,1:49:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.83,1:49:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.32,1:49:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.82,1:49:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all we can do?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.50,1:49:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.54,1:49:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.04,1:49:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.96,1:49:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing left for us to feel guilty about.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.54,1:49:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That we didn't do this and we didn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.86,1:49:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how the human ego likes guilt.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.33,1:49:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we don't have anything left to feel guilty about.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.15,1:49:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that going to be a tough evening?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.94,1:49:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we going to get by without anything to feel guilty about?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.28,1:49:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.04,1:50:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel guilty that I don't feel guilty about anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.16,1:50:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.62,1:50:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord, for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.52,1:50:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give him a good blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.00,1:50:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She says I have to bless everybody and then let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.24,1:50:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.10,1:50:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.36,1:50:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.20,1:50:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I adore you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.30,1:50:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In God's name I do bless thee.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.80,1:50:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.60,1:50:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.08,1:51:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.19,1:51:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.49,1:51:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Without you, the work would not, would not work.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.39,1:51:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.89,1:51:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Would not be what it is today.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.99,1:51:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to thank you, each and every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.29,1:51:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And thank you so much for your presence here.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.26,1:51:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.58,1:51:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.18,1:51:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.11,1:51:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at those beautiful flowers.
